## Recommended and Required Releases

The newest release is always recommended. The following Avid NEXIS | VFS releases are either recommended or required in the cases listed below.

According to Avid’s Customer Support Contract Terms and Conditions, customers are required to upgrade regularly to benefit from fixes and stability enhancements. All customers must plan to upgrade at least once per year.

An Avid NEXIS system (server) can be updated before the clients to allow server-only fixes to be deployed faster.

---

## What’s New in Avid NEXIS 2025.5.7

Avid NEXIS version 2025.5.7 is a patch release for **on-premises systems only**.

### Server Fixes

- **SSENG-46549, SSENG-46595, SSENG-46563**  
  Fixes a Storage Manager deadlock during shutdown that could prevent restart and cause Media Pack disconnections.

- **SSENG-46654**  
  Fixes slow Media Composer export operations caused by a scheduling issue in the Storage Manager read workflow.

---

## What’s New in Avid NEXIS 2025.5.6

Avid NEXIS version 2025.5.6 is a **client-only** patch release.

### Client Fixes

- **SSENG-45048**  
  Fixes Media Composer crashes on Intel Macs and Apple Silicon Macs running via Rosetta due to exported BOOST symbols.

---

## What’s New in Avid NEXIS 2025.5.5

Patch release for **on-premises systems only**.

### Server Fixes

- Storage Group and Workspace capacity display issues
- Broken documentation link in Management Console
- Index Server segmentation faults with File Delete Logging enabled
- Media Pack disconnections on mirrored systems
- Blank Connection Status page when only one active connection exists
- Certificate initialization errors causing HTTP 502

Windows 10 is no longer supported in this release.

---

## What’s New in Avid NEXIS 2025.10.0

Client-only release for on-premises systems and full Cloud kit release.

Includes:

- Ubuntu 24.04 client support
- Rocky Linux support for Cloud Storage
- Avid NEXIS | Remote
- Avid NEXIS Management API documentation
- Removal of CentOS installers
- Windows 10 end of qualification

---

